{"type":"message","id":"c2b10058","parentId":"8242791c","timestamp":"2026-05-18T06:42:10.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sed command ran but let me verify it actually changed the file correctly. The JSON structure was:\n```json\n\"capability-evolver\": {\n  \"enabled\": true\n}\n```\n\nThe sed pattern might not have matched correctly because the JSON has newlines and different spacing. Let me check the actual content.","thinkingSignature":"bcf7c43004d3017c4ef5d4e72273face52e87568f3c14d35475da9a90b0db7c5"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me verify the change worked:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_onpmqich25y3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A2 \"capability-evolver\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":10257,"output":121,"cacheRead":26290,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779086525045,"responseId":"0659e7bdfc1719a75adb76ecb063e529"}}
