{"type":"message","id":"a6554e50","parentId":"f60fd49d","timestamp":"2026-05-18T06:42:36.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The capability-evolver is under `.skills.entries.capability-evolver`, not `plugins.entries.capability-evolver`. So I need to patch `skills.entries.capability-evolver.enabled` to `false`.","thinkingSignature":"4eddfccee742bcc1aa60ec268627bad1e7ecc390ac0bc03215f98bdc982229f9"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！`capability-evolver` 在 `skills.entries.capability-evolver` 而不是 `plugins.entries`。让我修正它：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_two83o11abi0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# Set capability-evolver.enabled = False\nif 'skills' in config and 'entries' in config['skills']:\n    if 'capability-evolver' in config['skills']['entries']:\n        config['skills']['entries']['capability-evolver']['enabled'] = False\n        print('Set skills.entries.capability-evolver.enabled = False')\n    else:\n        print('capability-evolver not found in skills.entries')\nelse:\n    print('skills or entries not found')\n\nwith open('/home/halei/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\nprint('Saved.')\n\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11078,"output":274,"cacheRead":26290,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779086549837,"responseId":"0659e7d6776ae871b5c41811f932fd6d"}}
