{"type":"message","id":"2eccadc0","parentId":"9633d20f","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:07:53.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `plugins.entries.capability-evolver` doesn't exist, but `skills.entries.capability-evolver` does with `enabled: false`. The config was correctly patched.\n\nBut wait - I wonder if the plugin/skill path used by the capability-evolver is `plugins.entries` not `skills.entries`. Looking at the log output earlier, it was in `plugins.entries` section of the config. Let me check what the actual config structure looks like and whether `plugins.entries.capability-evolver` needs to be added as well.\n\nActually, looking at the original config output:\n```json\n\"plugins\": {\n    \"slots\": {\n      \"contextEngine\": \"lossless-claw\"\n    },\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"lossless-claw\": {...},\n      \"memory-core\": {...},\n      \"minimax\": {...},\n      \"feishu\": {...}\n    },\n    \"allow\": [...]\n}\n```\n\nThere's no `capability-evolver` in `plugins.entries`. It was only in `skills.entries`. So the capability-evolver is a skill, not a plugin in the `plugins.entries` sense.\n\nNow the skill is disabled. But the message was still sent. Maybe there's a cron job running it? Let me check the cron jobs more carefully.\n\nWait, I just realized something - the user sent the same \"啥情况\" message again (message_id om_x100b6f9fe81558c8c3c246afca1f2b6). This might be the same message being re-delivered. Or it could be a new message from the user asking what's going on.\n\nActually the key question is: does the user still receive the \"Capability Evolver 完成\" messages? Let me check the cron jobs that might be related to capability-evolver.\n\nActually, I think the user is asking \"啥情况\" in response to MY previous message (the one asking if they still get the messages after my fix). So they're probably just confirming they still see it or asking what the status is.\n\nLet me just verify the current state properly and tell the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"9ec3480a8ccc333cec04d0d5e6586c201ba7e58ee44e791d10d81692489fc9c2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了。配置里 `skills.entries.capability-evolver.enabled = false` 已经生效。让我再查一下是不是有 cron 在定时跑它。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h6thlvngqqxp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron list 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":8}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1694,"output":500,"cacheRead":43383,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779088053027,"responseId":"0659edb5c9d2d409e3d79c8e29afacde"}}
