{"type":"message","id":"fd37b599","parentId":"2727f604","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:08:49.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I found the real source. The Capability Evolver message is being sent by a custom script in `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/evolver.sh`. This is a standalone shell script that sends a Feishu message directly. It's not the capability-evolver skill/plugin at all - it's a custom backup script that sends notifications via `send-to-me.js`.\n\nSo the `skills.entries.capability-evolver` in the config is actually a completely different thing from this `evolver.sh` script. The evolver.sh is part of the `openclaw-backup` skill and sends messages using the Feishu API directly.\n\nLet me find the cron job that's triggering this evolver.sh script. The evolver.sh is at `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/evolver.sh` and it sends messages via `send-to-me.js`. Let me find if there's a cron running this.\n","thinkingSignature":"0e1e9f12cced2a0edf25e3eefeaecc25ffc377df02216ca1258494364b2b73ab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p7x90kqu46ux_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/evolver.sh 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2783,"output":245,"cacheRead":44532,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47560,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779088117834,"responseId":"0659edf64fde4f0ae57dfde330039edf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f8a1f12","parentId":"fd37b599","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:08:49.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_p7x90kqu46ux_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Capability Evolver Standalone Runner\n# 独立运行 evolver，单独发飞书通知\n\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-evolver.log\"\nEVOLVER_DIR=\"/home/halei/skills/capability-evolver\"\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting Capability Evolver...\"\n\n{\n  cd \"$EVOLVER_DIR\"\n  EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced node index.js run 2>&1\n  EVOLVE_EXIT=$?\n} > >(tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\")\n\necho \"[$(date)] Capability evolver finished with exit $EVOLVE_EXIT\"\n\n# ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\nSCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\nif [ $EVOLVE_EXIT -eq 0 ]; then\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"🧬 Capability Evolver 完成（exit 0）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nelse\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"⚠️ Capability Evolver 有错误（exit $EVOLVE_EXIT）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nfi\n# ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":20,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# Capability Evolver Standalone Runner\n# 独立运行 evolver，单独发飞书通知\n\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-evolver.log\"\nEVOLVER_DIR=\"/home/halei/skills/capability-evolver\"\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting Capability Evolver...\"\n\n{\n  cd \"$EVOLVER_DIR\"\n  EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced node index.js run 2>&1\n  EVOLVE_EXIT=$?\n} > >(tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\")\n\necho \"[$(date)] Capability evolver finished with exit $EVOLVE_EXIT\"\n\n# ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\nSCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\nif [ $EVOLVE_EXIT -eq 0 ]; then\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"🧬 Capability Evolver 完成（exit 0）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nelse\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"⚠️ Capabili