{"type":"message","id":"122ebfc2","parentId":"f61c03e4","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:14:31.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The backup script backs up:\n- `workspace/` → `workspace/` in the backup repo\n- `workspace-main/` → `workspace-main/` in the backup repo\n- Other workspace directories like `workspace-tts/`, `workspace-selector/`, etc. are NOT individually backed up separately\n\nBut looking at the OpenClaw config, there are multiple agents (main, tts, etc.) with their own workspaces. Let me check if workspace-tts is inside workspace/ or separate.\n\nActually, looking at the directory listing, `workspace-tts` is at the same level as `workspace`. So it's a separate directory that might not be backed up by the current script.\n\n\nThe backup script captures the main workspace and workspace-main, but I need to verify whether workspace-tts and the agents' individual workspaces under ~/.openclaw/agents/ are being included in the backup or if they're separate locations that need their own backup entries. So the current backup script is incomplete—it's only backing up the main workspace and workspace-main, but missing workspace-tts and potentially other agent workspaces that exist in the system. I should clarify this gap with the user rather than making assumptions about what needs to be included.\n","thinkingSignature":"7708232c98704d42b284380a499d0a57fd106fc62ee8e1634a750433ca37fd50"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n不完全是。看了一下备份脚本，它现在备份的是：\n\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/` → GitHub `workspace/`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace-main/` → GitHub `workspace-main/`\n\n但你还有这些 workspace 目录**没有单独备份**：\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/`\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace-selector/`\n- `~/.openclaw/agents/tts/workspace/`（tts agent 的 session 等）\n\n每个 agent 的 workspace 都在 `~/.openclaw/agents/<agent-id>/workspace/` 下，目前只有 `tts` 有独立 workspace，备份脚本没单独处理它。\n\n要我把它也加到备份里吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2203,