{"type":"message","id":"1f7eecfb","parentId":"5986ab98","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:15:25.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the agents that have their own workspaces are likely tts (since we saw workspace-tts in the listing), and maybe others. The agents (tts, main, etc.) are stored under ~/.openclaw/agents/. The agents have their own session files and possibly workspace directories.\n\nLet me check what's under each agent directory:\n","thinkingSignature":"1d06512d93a19f7ecb304d838850785417f6c84191e9e3905b93bbeaff528eec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4cr3oriyyxv1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for agent in ~/.openclaw/agents/*/; do\n  name=$(basename \"$agent\")\n  ws=\"$agent/workspace\"\n  if [ -d \"$ws\" ]; then\n    echo \"✓ $name/workspace exists\"\n    ls \"$ws\" | head -5\n  else\n    echo \"✗ $name/workspace NOT found\"\n  fi\ndone","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1788,"output":179,"cacheRead":50215,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52182,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779088515047,"responseId":"0659ef838487c1d3937145340fdc5712"}}
