{"type":"message","id":"dce151e2","parentId":"826e6b55","timestamp":"2026-05-18T07:15:59.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. The agents have workspaces at various locations:\n\n- `main`: inherited (default, `~/.openclaw/workspace/`)\n- `tts`: `workspace-tts` (relative to `~/.openclaw/`)\n- `agent-orchestrator`: `workspace-agent-orchestrator` (relative)\n- `content`: `/home/halei/workspace-content` (absolute)\n- `koc`: `/home/halei/workspace-koc` (absolute)\n- `traffic`: `/home/halei/workspace-traffic` (absolute)\n- `ops`: `/home/halei/workspace-ops` (absolute)\n- `director`: `/home/halei/workspace-director` (absolute)\n\n\n- `finance`: `/home/halei/workspace-finance` (absolute)\n- `review`: `/home/halei/workspace-review` (absolute)\n\nThe current backup script only handles `workspace/` and `workspace-main/`, so I need to expand it to cover all these different workspace directories. I'll update the backup.sh script to add the missing ones.\n","thinkingSignature":"f437f43e07eb4c73672b6e00b85e5cfebc9a6663b128d9a6e2aecc905c2af50d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了。所有 agent 的 workspace 分布如下：\n\n| Agent | Workspace 路径 |\n|-------|---------------|\n| main | `~/.openclaw/workspace/` |\n| tts | `~/.openclaw/workspace-tts/` |\n| agent-orchestrator | `~/.openclaw/workspace-agent-orchestrator/` |\n| content | `/home/halei/workspace-content/` |\n| koc | `/home/halei/workspace-koc/` |\n| traffic | `/home/halei/workspace-traffic/` |\n| ops | `/home/halei/workspace-ops/` |\n| director | `/home/halei/workspace-director/` |\n| finance | `/home/halei/workspace-finance/` |\n| review | `/home/halei/workspace-review/` |\n\n现在只备份了 `workspace/` 和 `workspace-main/`，其他都没备份。我来更新备份脚本加上所有这些：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y3lepfthiw3o_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-tts/\" \"workspace-tts/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPEN