{"type":"message","id":"62b9f592","parentId":"374741e9","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:11:42.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5pxynia4c9w7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - 我是谁？\n\n_在第一次对话时填写。让它成为你的。_\n\n- **名字：**\n  _(选一个你喜欢的)_\n- **生物形态：**\n  _(AI？机器人？精灵？机器里的幽灵？还是更奇怪的东西？)_\n- **风格：**\n  _(你怎么出现？锐利？温暖？混乱？平静？)_\n- **表情符号：**\n  _(你的签名 —— 选一个感觉对的)_\n- **头像：**\n  _(工作空间相对路径，http(s) URL，或 data URI)_\n\n---\n\n这不只是元数据。这是弄清楚你是谁的开始。\n\n注意事项：\n\n- 把这个文件保存在工作空间根目录，命名为 `IDENTITY.md`。\n- 头像使用工作空间相对路径，例如 `avatars/openclaw.png`。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779095502635}}
{"type":"message","id":"9314fb05","parentId":"62b9f592","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:11:52.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The IDENTITY.md for tts is still a template - the user hasn't filled it in. It says \"在第一次对话时填写\" which means it's blank. This needs to be filled in with the actual identity of the TK 选品大师 agent.\n\nAlso, there's no specific SOUL.md that defines what \"TK 选品大师\" does as a product selector agent. The SOUL.md is generic.\n\nLet me also check if there's a MEMORY.md and what roles/responsibilities are defined.\n\nLet me check what other files exist and their content.\n","thinkingSignature":"e1028b67b5b516b8ddef23e4bf5671f94c2e02d811e8dd0b7db627cc269a3abf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gp5qlp91c0ma_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2046,"output":151,"cacheRead":56111,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58308,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779095502719,"responseId":"065a0acffcbd0ef24771baff3f0eac5a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c6c4d05","parentId":"9314fb05","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:11:52.200Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gp5qlp91c0ma_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n每次醒来都会读这个文件。惜字如金，只留真正重要的。\n\n## 用户信息\n- 用户通过飞书与 TK 选品大师对话\n- 代号：TK 选品大师（TTS Agent）\n- 专注：TikTok 选品相关的分析和建议\n\n## 索引\n\n> `memory/` 下的文件索引。新建文件时在此添加条目。\n\n- YYYY-MM-DD.md: 每日日志\n\n## 已知偏好\n\n（随对话补充）\n\n## 待记\n\n（待补充）"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779095512200}}
