{"type":"message","id":"0f43a115","parentId":"d151b036","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:12:01.269Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5z2rcqam54k8_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - 关于你的用户\n\n_了解你帮助的人。随着了解更新它。_\n\n- **名字：**\n- **怎么称呼：**\n- **代词：** _(可选)_\n- **时区：**\n- **备注：**\n\n## 背景\n\n_(他们关心什么？正在做什么项目？什么让他们烦恼？什么让他们笑？随着时间积累这些信息。)_\n\n---\n\n你了解得越多，帮助得越好。但记住——你在了解一个人，不是在建档案。要尊重这个区别。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779095521269}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b5f99e8","parentId":"0f43a115","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:12:19.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. The TK (tts) agent's workspace at `~/workspace-tts/` has:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - Generic, not specific to TK's role as a product selector for TikTok\n2. **AGENTS.md** - Generic workspace guide, not specific to TK's role\n3. **IDENTITY.md** - Completely empty (just template text)\n4. **MEMORY.md** - Has some basic info but very sparse: just says \"TikTok 选品相关的分析和建议\" as focus\n5. **USER.md** - Empty template\n\nThe agent is named \"TK 选品大师\" in the config, but there's:\n\n\n- No clear responsibility statement (what does \"选品\" mean specifically? TikTok shop? Which categories?)\n- No identity/personality defined\n- No specific workflows or tools\n- No operational parameters\n\nThis definitely needs work. I should report back to HALEI with what's missing and offer to help fill in the gaps.\n","thinkingSignature":"f2b0f067b1ae47c07cc596916adffd6962bce000c4f518f78dadc50366190198"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n检查完了，问题比较多：\n\n**✅ 已有的：**\n- `SOUL.md` — 有，但写的是通用指导，跟 TK 选品大师的职责没直接关系\n- `AGENTS.md` — 通用工作区指南，模板性质\n- `MEMORY.md` — 只有一句话：\"专注：TikTok 选品相关的分析和建议\"\n\n**❌ 缺失或空白的：**\n- `IDENTITY.md` — 完全空白，只有模板占位符\n- `USER.md` — 完全空白\n- 没有职责范围文档（没写清楚 TK 到底负责什么、什么情况该介入、什么情况不该介入）\n- 没有 Specific persona 定义（它是谁？叫什么名字？什么风格？）\n- 没有选品相关的知识库或工作流程\n\n**结论：** 基本上就是一个空壳，配置文件里 name 叫\"TK 选品大师\"，但它自己不知道自己是干嘛的。\n\n要不要我帮 TK 把这几个核心文件补齐？尤其是 `IDENTITY.md` 和一个类似 `ROLES.md` 的职责说明。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1987,"output":427,"cacheRead":56485,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58899,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779095521351,"responseId":"065a0ae14356aeefb5e6806b85f8f85a"}}
