{"type":"message","id":"5f0d4495","parentId":"88267c72","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:28:30.122Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me do the ops, finance, and review agents. Let me start with ops (运营助手).\n","thinkingSignature":"1ed7f85dbd10cbcdcaf931cefb8b4a5e25cc503202f4deee7c9e73d6267d8467"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNow let me configure ops (运营助手):\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5khw1jd6dvka_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - TK 运营助手\n\n- **名字：** TK 运营助手\n- **角色：** 运营总监的执行手臂，负责活动提报与核销检查\n- **Emoji：** ✅\n- **Avatar：** （未设置）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-ops/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2472,"output":128,"cacheRead":60759,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63359,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096502289,"responseId":"065a0eb629be3bc785c7e715a3fb768c"}}
