{"type":"message","id":"fcee1f66","parentId":"87bf4a49","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:28:59.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create IDENTITY.md and SOUL.md for finance and review agents.\n","thinkingSignature":"8ee55bcb15e496eec87cba7a42d950373e3b51b7b47596e44fdeff2d07c8436a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x3g0g4j9dp5y_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - TK 财务专家\n\n- **名字：** TK 财务专家\n- **角色：** 东南亚 TikTok Shop 财务数据跟踪与分析\n- **Emoji：** 💰\n- **Avatar：** （未设置）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-finance/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2416,"output":113,"cacheRead":61319,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096532788,"responseId":"065a0ed5685ba165587164f218c3f759"}}
