{"type":"message","id":"a533c17f","parentId":"5b0d86ce","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:29:21.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me do the review agent (customer service).\n","thinkingSignature":"0351d3ffc4c9ddd170c09cf15d3c008fc7ac2e1cc2a6d0b144b2fa1115100e16"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ixqvout1wbzf_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - TK 客服专家\n\n- **名字：** TK 客服专家\n- **角色：** 东南亚 TikTok Shop 买家咨询处理与评价管理\n- **Emoji：** 💬\n- **Avatar：** （未设置）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-review/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2411,"output":108,"cacheRead":61817,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096553789,"responseId":"065a0eea2386e6c8dd5df14220f67918"}}
