{"type":"message","id":"ae01623b","parentId":"9be6973c","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:30:00.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the USER.md files for each agent and make sure the MEMORY.md files have basic info. Also, I should update the AGENTS.md files to be in Chinese. Actually, the AGENTS.md is a template that doesn't really need to be customized per agent - it's a general workspace guide. What matters most is the SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md.\n\nLet me also update the USER.md files so each agent knows basic context.\n","thinkingSignature":"bd264da73e416cd6f7b1f701e6795ed5be255eeb145189214d6ef3b658cbef16"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_llf7m1xk79sq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# USER.md - 关于 HALEI\n\n- **名字：** HALEI\n- **怎么称呼：** HALEI\n- **时区：** Asia/Shanghai（GMT+8）\n- **备注：** TK 跨境电商团队负责人，管理东南亚新马泰5个 TikTok Shop 站点\n\n## 背景\n\n- 主营东南亚 TikTok Shop（新加坡、马来西亚、泰国）\n- 团队有多个专业 Agent：选品大师、内容专家、达人专家、投流专家、运营总监、运营助手、财务专家、客服专家\n- 通过飞书与各个 Agent 协同工作\n- 希望 Agent 能主动发现问题、及时汇报、清晰表达\n\n## 风格\n\n- 高效直接，讨厌废话\n- 需要数据支撑，不喜欢拍脑袋的结论\n- 喜欢主动汇报而不是被追问","path":"/home/halei/workspace-director/USER.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2440,"output":302,"cacheRead":62313,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096585287,"responseId":"065a0f097f002795220bf45d9b4ca40f"}}
