{"type":"message","id":"209f505a","parentId":"d48c66be","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:30:19.177Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also check if content, koc, and traffic have their files properly set up. These are the other agents that are active. Let me quickly check what they have.Actually, let me first report back to the user on what I've done for the four agents (director, ops, finance, review). Then I should also quickly check content, koc, traffic, and tts to see if they need work too.\n\nActually the user said tts is already being debugged with some processes configured. So let me focus on the others.\n\nLet me quickly check what content, koc, traffic look like.\n","thinkingSignature":"ca7a2e2e66349f226657c194774c30d63ab954a71e8c873da2c9741463e2729b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n同时我也检查一下 content、koc、traffic 的状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ftimo5ig3jjl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for ws in content koc traffic; do\n  echo \"=== $ws ===\"\n  cat ~/workspace-$ws/IDENTITY.md 2>/dev/null | head -6\n  echo \"SOUL lines: $(wc -l < ~/workspace-$ws/SOUL.md 2>/dev/null || echo 0)\"\n  echo \"\"\ndone","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2159,"output":246,"cacheRead":62942,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65347,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096607375,"responseId":"065a0f2059af34cd858be2f8f958fc1f"}}
