{"type":"message","id":"ca4ccf06","parentId":"77ab1017","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:31:50.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the traffic agent. It already has an IDENTITY.md but let me check if it needs a proper one for the TK context. The traffic agent's IDENTITY.md shows \"小光\" with some personality, but it doesn't say it's specifically for TK TikTok Shop. Let me update it.\n","thinkingSignature":"de3dbeccddc2326d115ef339751da1ab23e0f33f24b9981ee836bf876eb0f148"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b4gxivxh0hnv_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - TK 投流专家\n\n- **名字：** TK 投流专家\n- **角色：** 东南亚 TikTok Shop 广告投放与流量运营专家\n- **Emoji：** 🚀\n- **Avatar：** （未设置）","path":"/home/halei/workspace-traffic/IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2174,"output":163,"cacheRead":64806,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096696854,"responseId":"065a0f7926275d259f4269e8e89a5f41"}}
