{"type":"message","id":"242fb81a","parentId":"5b773122","timestamp":"2026-05-18T09:32:18.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the SOUL.md for the tts (TK选品大师) since we saw it was also mostly a template. But actually, the user said the tts is \"正在调试\"，所以可能已经有了一些配置了，我就不动它了。\n\nLet me also update the USER.md for workspace-traffic (it already exists, let me check).\n","thinkingSignature":"e52370e55c20fd8786174cd47cf8c6c8bdcdcbfb047267b184becf3f667ed72e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j911ivsy1m5u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp /home/halei/workspace-director/USER.md /home/halei/workspace-traffic/USER.md 2>/dev/null; echo \"Done\"\n# Also copy to agent-orchestrator\nmkdir -p ~/workspace-agent-orchestrator 2>/dev/null\nls ~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/SOUL.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"No SOUL.md found\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2563,"output":190,"cacheRead":64981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67734,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779096730734,"responseId":"065a0f9b41a5282b1108085c32b12048"}}
